'''Vobos''' was a loctation on [[Tammuz-an/Legends|Tammuz-an]]. A ship owned by [[Joa Pqis]] called the ''[[Star Hummer]]'' was registered there.

==Behind the scenes==
[[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', confirmed in [[June]] [[2015]] that Vobos was a location on Tammuz-an.<ref name="Email">{{EmailCite|email=File:EAOC discussion.jpg|creator=Jason Fry|date=2015-06-30}}</ref>

